{"title":"OGC Service Dashboard Instructions","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"# OGC Services
This dashboard is for viewing standard O2 metrics provided by the OGC apps.

Click on a visualization or slice of data to interactively browse metrics.

To save changes to this dashboard, follow [the instructions](https://github.com/radiantbluetechnologies/oc2s-metrics-dashboards/blob/dev/README.md)."},"aggs":[]}
